data.description: LOOKING FOR PEACE & QUIET?? Well search no more, this home is in a Cul-de-sac and backs up to woods! This is the only 24hr. guard gated community in Jacksonville. This adorable home features tall ceilings, indoor laundry room, & the oversized master bedroom is separated from the others (opposite sides of house). Master bedroom has tray ceilings and French doors leading to a screened in patio that backs up to nature at its finest! The Master en-suite has his & her vanities/closets with a separate garden tub. The eat in kitchen also gives access to the screened in patio which is fantastic for entertaining and family events. The spacious kitchen overlooks the living room & has a wood burning fireplace. The upstairs bedroom/bath is private due to it being the only room on the floor!
